<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- saved from url=(0050)file:///C:/Users/lukek/Downloads/og-card-scan.html -->
<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    width: 1200px;
    height: 630px;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0f;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 60px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Background glow */
  .glow1 {
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #6c63ff33, transparent 70%);
    top: -100px; left: -100px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .glow2 {
    position: absolute;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #ff658422, transparent 70%);
    bottom: -100px; right: 200px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Grid lines */
  .grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(108,99,255,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(108,99,255,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
  }

  /* Left content */
  .left {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .logo span { color: #6c63ff; }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #ff6584);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  h1 span { color: #6c63ff; }

  p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #8080b0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #c0c0e0;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #9b85ff);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Right — phone mockup */
  .right {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .phone {
    width: 240px;
    height: 460px;
    background: #13131e;
    border-radius: 36px;
    border: 2px solid #2a2a3f;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px #ffffff08, inset 0 1px 0 #ffffff10;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .phone-notch {
    width: 80px; height: 20px;
    background: #0a0a0f;
    border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .phone-screen {
    padding: 8px 14px 14px;
  }

  .phone-logo {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .phone-logo span { color: #6c63ff; }

  .phone-upload {
    background: #1a1a26;
    border: 2px dashed #2a2a3f;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px 10px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .phone-upload .icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .phone-upload .title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .phone-upload .sub { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #6060a0; }

  .phone-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 9px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #ff6584);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .phone-card {
    background: #1a1a26;
    border: 1px solid #252535;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .phone-card .biz { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .phone-card .trade { font-size: 0.6rem; color: #6c63ff; margin-bottom: 6px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; }
  .phone-card .chips { display: flex; gap: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .phone-card .chip { background: #252535; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 0.55rem; color: #c0c0e0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; }

  /* URL bar */
  .url {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 60px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #3a3a5a;
  }
  .url span { color: #6c63ff; }
</style>
<link href="./og-card-scan_files/css2" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<div class="grid"></div>
<div class="glow1"></div>
<div class="glow2"></div>

<div class="left">
  <div class="logo">i<span>Tabs</span></div>
  <div class="badge">Free for Perth Tradies</div>
  <h1>Scan your card.<br>Get your <span>quote page</span><br>in minutes.</h1>
  <p>Take a photo of your business card — our AI reads it,<br>builds your widget, emails you the link. Done.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div> Scan card</div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div> Preview</div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div> Get your link</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="right">
  <div class="phone">
    <div class="phone-notch"></div>
    <div class="phone-screen">
      <div class="phone-logo">i<span>Tabs</span></div>
      <div class="phone-upload">
        <div class="icon">📇</div>
        <div class="title">Drop your business card</div>
        <div class="sub">We'll read it automatically</div>
      </div>
      <div class="phone-btn">📸 Take a photo now</div>
      <div class="phone-card">
        <div class="biz">Smith Plumbing</div>
        <div class="trade">✓ read &nbsp; Plumber — Joondalup</div>
        <div class="chips">
          <div class="chip">Blocked drains</div>
          <div class="chip">Hot water</div>
          <div class="chip">Gas leaks</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="url">itabs.ai/<span>scan</span></div>



</body></html>